    51: '<button class="choice" id="choice-51-60" value="60">Grab the kid on the left</button><button class="choice" id="choice-51-65" value="65">Grab the kid on the right</button><button class="choice" id="choice-51-63" value="63">Let the kids go by</button>',
    52: '<button class="choice" id="choice-52-58" value="58">Continue</button>',
    53: '<button class="choice" id="choice-53-42" value="42">Turn Gu\'dal over to the gendarmes</button><button class="choice" id="choice-53-47" value="47">Fight</button>',
    54: '<h2>The End</h2>',
    55: '<button class="choice" id="choice-55-76" value="76">Suggest that you would be more useful outside the gates, where you could use your torch if need be</button><button class="choice" id="choice-55-78" value="78">Follow Sergei into the officer\'s quarters</button>',
    56: '<button class="choice" id="choice-56-66" value="66">Say "Of course you have a saying about that. How many times have you said it? When has it been true? No, you must abandon your plans of terror and revolution. I won\'t let you take so many lives, nor let you destroy an entire city block"</button><button class="choice" id="choice-56-71" value="71">Say "I volunteer my body for your cause. My brother fought for the Paris commue, and I\'d be proud to fight for the emancipation of your people"</button><button class="choice" id="choice-56-75" value="75">Say "You need to control the escape of the gnomes onto the surface, do you? Well I\'ve got an idea. It involves a hot-air balloon, some guns, and a spyglass"</button>',
    57: '<h2>The End</h2>',
    58: '<button class="choice" id="choice-58-67" value="67">Inform him that you are here to act as an ambassador for the goblins, and intend to seek resolution by means of words</button><button class="choice" id="choice-58-72" value="72">Escape your cell through the open window and join the gnomish Aboveground</button><button class="choice" id="choice-58-77" value="77">Verbally express your discontent with the gnomish Aboveground\'s threats upon your health, then shout for your guard to capture the interloper</button>',
    59: '<h2>The End</h2>',
    60: '<h2>The End</h2>',
    61: '<button class="choice" id="choice-61-68" value="68">Continue</button>',
    62: '<button class="choice" id="choice-62-70" value="70">Stay around and see your plot through to its end</button><button class="choice" id="choice-62-74" value="74">Give up on this whole adventure, state that you\'ve had your fun but that it\'s time for you to return to your home on the surface</button>',
    63: '<h2>The End</h2>',
